tool_description: An api that exposes the top 10 highest paid athletes since 1990, this api needs to specify the parameter year
name: The World's Highest-Paid Athletes 1990/2023
title: The World's Highest-Paid Athletes 1990/2023

api_list.name: Get top paid athletes in a specific year and a rank
api_list.description: An Api that exposes a filtered list of a specific year with a specific rank like for example the top paid athlete in 2023 is Cristiano Ronaldo with rank 1
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://the-worlds-highest-paid-athletes-1990-2023.p.rapidapi.com/2023/1"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "the-worlds-highest-paid-athletes-1990-2023.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
